    • findByFridgeIdAndGroceryItemId

      @Query("SELECT g FROM GroceryItemFridge g WHERE g.id.fridgeId = :fridgeId AND g.id.groceryItemId = :groceryItemId ORDER BY g.expirationDate ASC") List<GroceryItemFridge> findByFridgeIdAndGroceryItemId(Long fridgeId, Long groceryItemId)
      Finds all GroceryItemFridge objects for a given fridge and grocery item, sorted by their expiration date in ascending order.
      Parameters:
      fridgeId - the ID of the fridge to search for
      groceryItemId - the ID of the grocery item to search for
      Returns:
      a list of all GroceryItemFridge objects found in the fridge, sorted by expiration date

    • deleteByFridgeIdAndGroceryItemIdAndTimestamp

      @Modifying @Query("DELETE FROM GroceryItemFridge g WHERE g.id.fridgeId = :fridgeId AND g.id.groceryItemId = :groceryItemId AND g.id.timestamp = :timestamp") void deleteByFridgeIdAndGroceryItemIdAndTimestamp(Long fridgeId, Long groceryItemId, LocalDateTime timestamp)

      Updates the amount of a specific GroceryItemFridge object based on the given fridge ID, grocery item ID, and timestamp.
